OL,3,CVolunteer suicide responders say call-
OL,4,Couts have increased 'dramatically'
OL,6,FThe South Shields Volunteer Life
OL,7,FBrigade (VLB) is responding to more
OL,8,Fcall-outs related to mental health
OL,9,Fcrises than ever before.
OL,11,FSteven West, Brigade Captain, has been
OL,12,Fvolunteering for the Brigade for 16
OL,13,Fyears.
OL,15,FHe told ITV Tyne Tees that when he
OL,16,Fstarted, there were four or five call
OL,17,Fouts a month - now there are two or
OL,18,Fthree a week.
