OL,3,CVolunteer suicide responders say call-
OL,4,Couts have increased 'dramatically'
OL,6,FHe said: "The amount of call-outs,
OL,7,Fespecially due to mental health
OL,8,Fthroughout the UK, has dramatically
OL,9,Fincreased, so coastguard teams and
OL,10,Fvolunteer life brigades are getting
OL,11,Fcalled out more often than the past."
OL,13,FOn average the South Shields VLB is
OL,14,Fcalled out 120 times a year.
OL,16,FThe duration of the call-outs can last
OL,17,Ffrom an hour, up to two or three hours.
