OL,3,CVolunteer suicide responders say call-
OL,4,Couts have increased 'dramatically'
OL,6,FMr West added: "That can be for
OL,7,Fanybody in the water, anybody on the
OL,8,Fedge of a cliff or in a bay cut off by
OL,9,Fthe tide.
OL,11,F"Obviously access and extracting the
OL,12,Fcasualty from that locations falls to
OL,13,Fus."
OL,15,FOn Saturday 25 May, supporters walked
OL,16,Fthe coast from the Brigade Watch House
OL,17,Fin South Shields to the Tommy statue
OL,18,Fin Seaham and back.
OL,20,FThe 32 mile walk aimed to raise funds
OL,21,Ffor the VLB.
