OL,3,CVolunteer suicide responders say call-
OL,4,Couts have increased 'dramatically'
OL,6,FWalk organiser, Angie Comerford, who
OL,7,Fruns Hebburn Helps foodbank, has been
OL,8,Forganising the walk for four years.
OL,10,FShe told ITV Tyne Tees: "It comes off
OL,11,Fthe back of, sadly, the mental health
OL,12,Fstate in the area.
OL,14,F"They're out in all hours, it doesn't
OL,15,Fmatter what day of the year or what
OL,16,Fthe weather's like, they are out. Real
OL,17,Flife heroes."
OL,19,FThe average running costs for the
OL,20,Fcharity are around #26,000 a year.
